"De Funkschoon CONVERT() gifft en Ümwanneln vun en Maatsysteem na en anner ut."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2088
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported mass units: g (gram), sg (pieces), lbm (pound), u (atomic mass), "
"ozm (ounce), stone, ton, grain, pweight (pennyweight), hweight "
"(hundredweight)."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Masseenheiten: g (Gramm), sg (Stück), lbm (Pund), u (Atoommass), "
"ozm (Unz), stone, ton (Tünn), grain, pweight (pennyweight), hweight "
"(Zentner)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2089
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported distance units: m (meter), in (inch), ft (feet), mi (mile), Nmi "
"(nautical mile), ang (Angstrom), parsec, lightyear."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Längdeneenheiten: m (Meter), in (Toll), ft (Foot), mi (Miel), Nmi "
"(Nautisch Miel), ang (Angström), parsec, lightyear (Lichtjohr)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported pressure units: Pa (Pascal), atm (atmosphere), mmHg (mm of "
"Mercury), psi, Torr."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Druckeenheiten: Pa, atm (phys. Atmosfeer), mmHg (mm "
"Quecksülversüül), psi (Pundkraft/Toll²), Torr (= mmHg)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported force units: N (Newton), dyn, pound."
msgstr "Ünnerstütt Knööveenheiten: N (Newton), dyn, pound."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported energy units: J (Joule), e (erg), c (Thermodynamic calorie), cal "
"(IT calorie), eV (electronvolt), HPh (Horsepower-hour), Wh (Watt-hour), flb "
"(foot-pound), BTU."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Energie-Eenheiten: J (Joule), e (erg), c (Thermodünaamsch "
"Kalorie), cal (IT Kalorie), eV (Elektronenvolt), HPh (Peerstärk-Stunn), Wh "
"(Wattstunn), flb (Foot-Pund), BTU."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported power units: W (Watt), HP (horsepower), PS (Pferdestaerke)."
msgstr "Ünnerstütt Knööveenheiten: W (Watt), HP (Horsepower), PS (Peerstärk)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2094
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported magnetism units: T (Tesla), ga (Gauss)."
msgstr "Ünnerstütt magneetsch Eenheiten: T (Tesla), ga (Gauss)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2095
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported temperature units: C (Celsius), F (Fahrenheit), K (Kelvin)."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Temperatuur-Eenheiten: C (Celsius), F (Fahrenheit), K (Kelvin)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported volume units: l (liter), tsp (teaspoon), tbs (tablespoon), oz "
"(ounce liquid), cup, pt (pint), qt (quart), gal (gallon), barrel, m3 (cubic "
"meter), mi3 (cubic mile), Nmi3 (cubic Nautical mile), in3 (cubic inch), ft3 "
"(cubic foot), yd3 (cubic yard), GRT or regton (gross register ton)."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Ruumeenheiten: l (Liter), tsp (Teelöpel), tbs (Eetlöpel), oz "
"(Fletig-Unz), cup (Tass), pt (Pint), qt (Quart), gal (Galloon), barrel, m3 "
"(Kubikmeter), mi3 (Kubikmiel), Nmi3 (Kubikseemiel), in3 (Kubiktoll), ft3 "
"(Kubikfoot), yd3 (Kubik-Yard), GRT oder regton (Bruttoregistertünn)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported area units: m2 (square meter), mi2 (square mile), Nmi2 (square "
"Nautical mile), in2 (square inch), ft2 (square foot), yd2 (square yard), "
"acre, ha (hectare)."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütte Rebeeteenheiten: m2 (Quadraatmeter), mi2 (Quadraatmiel), Nmi "
"(Quadraat nautisch Miel), in2 (Quadraattoll), ft2 (Quadraatfoot), yd2 "
"(Quadraat-Yard), acre, ha (Hektar)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Supported speed units: m/s (meters per second), m/h (meters per hour), mph "
"(miles per hour), kn (knot)."
msgstr ""
"Ünnerstütt Gauheit-Eenheiten: m/s (Meter per Sekunn), m/h (Meter per Stunn), "
"mph (Mielen per Stunn), kn (Knütt)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:2099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For metric units any of the following prefixes can be used: E (exa, 1E+18), "
"P (peta, 1E+15), T (tera, 1E+12), G (giga, 1E+09), M (mega, 1E+06), k (kilo, "
"1E+03), h (hecto, 1E+02), e (dekao, 1E+01), d (deci, 1E-01), c (centi, "
"1E-02), m (milli, 1E-03), u (micro, 1E-06), n (nano, 1E-09), p (pico, "
"1E-12), f (femto, 1E-15), a (atto, 1E-18)."
msgstr ""
"För metersch Eenheiten laat sik de nakamen Prefixen bruken: E (exa, 1E+18), "
"P (peta, 1E+15), T (tera, 1E+12), G (giga, 1E+09), M (mega, 1E+06), k (kilo, "
"1E+03), h (hekto, 1E+02), e (deka, 1E+01), d (dezi, 1E-01), c (zenti, "
"1E-02), m (milli, 1E-03), u (mikro, 1E-06), n (nano, 1E-09), p (piko, "
"1E-12), f (femto, 1E-15), a (atto, 1E-18)."

