#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The COMPOUND() function returns the value of an investment, given the "
"principal, nominal interest rate, compounding frequency and time. For "
"example: $5000 at 12% interest compounded quarterly for 5 years will become "
"COMPOUND(5000;0.12;4;5) or $9030.56."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon COMPOUND() gifft den Weert vun en Geldanlaag torüch, fastleggt "
"dör Startbedrag, nominaal Tinssatz, Optinsperiood un Tiet. 5000 Dollar a.B., "
"de elk Viddeljohr för fief Johr mit 12% optinst warrt, maakt "
"COMPOUND(5000;0.12;4;5) oder 9030,56 Dollar."

