#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:3580
#, no-c-format
msgid "FV_ANNUITY"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The FV_ANNUITY() function returns the future value of a stream of payments "
"given the amount of the payment, the interest rate and the number of "
"periods. For example: If you receive $500 per year for 20 years, and invest "
"it at 8%, the total after 20 years will be FV_annuity(500;0.08;20) or "
"$22,880.98. This function assumes that payments are made at the end of each "
"period."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon FV_ANNUITY() gifft den tokamen Weert vun en fast Geldstroom "
"torüch, angeven dör de Betahlen, den Tinssatz un de Tall vun Perioden. Wenn "
"Een a.B. twintig Johr lang 500 Dollar in't Johr kriggt un se mit 8% Tinsen "
"anleggt, gifft dat na 20 Johren tosamen en FV_annuity(500;0.08;20) oder "
"22880,98 Dollar. Disse Funkschoon vermoodt de Utbetahlen an't Enn vun elk "
"Periood."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid "FV_ANNUITY(amount;interest;periods)"
msgstr "FV_ANNUITY(Bedrag; Tins;Perioden)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:3590 functions.docbook:4075
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment per period"
msgstr "Utbetahlen per Periood"

