#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4044
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>PV</title>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4045
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PV() function returns the present value of an investment -- the value "
"today of a sum of money in the future, given the rate of interest or "
"inflation. For example if you need $1166.40 for your new computer and you "
"want to buy it in two years while earning 8% interest, you need to start "
"with PV(1166.4;0.08;2) or $1000."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon PV() gifft den aktuellen Weert vun en Geldanlaag torüch. Dat "
"is de Weert vundaag vun en Geldsumm in de Tokunft, fastleggt dör Tins oder "
"Inflatschoon. Wenn Een a.B. 1166,40 Dollar för en niegen Reekner bruukt un "
"em in twee Johren köpen will, bruukt he bi en Tinssatz vun 8% nu "
"PV(1166.4;0.08;2) oder 1000 Dollar."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4050
#, no-c-format
msgid "PV(future value;rate;periods)"
msgstr "PV(Tokamen Weert;Tins;Perioden)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:4054 functions.docbook:4099
#, no-c-format
msgid "Future value"
msgstr "Tokamen Weert"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4059
#, no-c-format
msgid "PV(1166.4;0.08;2) equals 1000"
msgstr "PV(1166,4; 0,08; 2) gifft \"1000\" torüch"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4065
#, no-c-format
msgid "PV_ANNUITY"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PV_ANNUITY() function returns the present value of an annuity or stream "
"of payments. For example: a \"million dollar\" lottery ticket that pays "
"$50,000 a year for 20 years, with an interest rate of 5%, is actually worth "
"PV_ANNUITY(50000;0.05;20) or $623,111. This function assumes that payments "
"are made at the end of each period."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon PV_ANNUITY() gifft den aktuellen Weert vun en Rent oder en "
"Geldstroom ut. En \"Een Million\"-Lotterieschien mit en Tinssatz vun 5% a."
"B., de twintig Johr lang 50000 Dollar in't Johr utbetahlt, is nu "
"PV_ANNUITY(50000;0,05;20) oder 623,111 Dollar weert. Disse Funkschoon "
"vermoodt de Utbetahlen an't Enn vun elk Periood."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4071
#, no-c-format
msgid "PV_ANNUITY(amount;interest;periods)"
msgstr "PV_ANNUITY(Bedrag; Tins; Perioden)"

#. Tag: para
