#, no-c-format
msgid "ZERO_COUPON"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ZERO_COUPON() function calculates the value of a zero-coupon (pure "
"discount) bond. For example: if the interest rate is 10%, a $1000 bond that "
"matures in 20 years is worth ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) or $148.64."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon ZERO_COUPON() reekt den Weert vun en Nullkuponanlehn (aftinst "
"Anlehn) ut. Bispill: Wenn de Tinssatz 10% is, denn is en Anlehn vun 1000 "
"Dollar, de na 20 Johren tahlbor is, ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) oder 148,64 "
"Dollar weert."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4432
#, no-c-format
msgid "ZERO_COUPON(face value;rate;years)"
msgstr "ZERO_COUPON(Nennweert;Tins;Johren)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4441
#, no-c-format
msgid "ZERO_COUPON(1000;.1;20) equals 148.64"
msgstr "ZERO_COUPON(1000;0,1;20) gifft \"148,64\" torüch"

