#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:7411
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMA"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The SUMA() function calculates the sum of all the values given as "
"parameters. You can calculate the sum of a range SUMA(A1:B5) or a list of "
"values like SUMA(12;5;12.5). If a parameter contains text or the boolean "
"value FALSE it is counted as 0, if a parameter evaluates to TRUE it is "
"counted as 1."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon SUMA() reekt de Summ vun all as Parameters angeven Weerten ut. "
"Een kann de Summ vun en Rebeet SUM(A1:B5) oder en List vun Weerten liek "
"SUM(12;5;12.5) utreken. Wenn en Parameter Text oder den boolsch Weert "
"\"falsch\" bargt, warrt dit as \"0\" tellt, wenn en Parameter \"wohr\" is, "
"denn as \"1\"."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7424
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMA(12;5; 7) equals 24"
msgstr "SUMA(12;5; 7) gifft 24 torüch"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7427
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMA(12.5; 2; TRUE) equals 15.5"
msgstr "SUMA(12.5; 2; wohr) gifft 15.5 torüch"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:7440
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMIF"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The SUMIF() function calculates the sum of all values given as parameters "
"which match the criteria. The sum range is optional. If not supplied, the "
"values in the check range are summed. The length of the check range should "
"be equal or less than the length of the sum range."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon SUMIF() reekt de Summ vun all as Parameters angeven Weerten "
"ut, de op de Bedingen passen. Dat Summrebeet is optschonaal. Ahn Angaav "
"warrt de Weerten binnen dat Pröövrebeet tosamentellt. De Längde vun't "
"Pröövrebeet schall liek oder lütter as de Längde vun't Summrebeet wesen."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7446
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMIF(checkrange;criteria;sumrange)"
msgstr "SUMIF(Rebeet;Bedingen;Summrebeet)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:7450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check range"
msgstr "Pröövrebeet"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:7452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sum range"
msgstr "Summrebeet"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7455
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMIF(A1:A4;\">1\") sums all values in range A1:A4 which match >1"
msgstr ""
"SUMIF(A1:A4;\">1\") tellt all Weerten binnen Rebeet A1:A4 tosamen, de >1 sünd"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"SUMIF(A1:A4;\"=0\";B1:B4) sums all values in range B1:B4 if the "
"corresponding value in A1:A4 matches =0"
msgstr ""
"SUMIF(A1:A4;\"=0\";B1:B4) tell all Weerten binnen Rebeet B1:B4 tosamen, wenn "
"de tohören Weert in A1:A4 =0 is"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:7470
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMSQ"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The SUMSQ() function calculates the sum of all the squares of values given "
"as parameters. You can calculate the sum of a range SUMSQ(A1:B5) or a list "
"of values like SUMSQ(12;5;12.5)."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon SUMSQ() reekt de Summ vun all Quadraten vun de as Parameters "
"angeven Weerten ut. Een kann de Summ vun en Rebeet SUMSQ(A1:B5) oder en List "
"vun Weerten liek SUMSQ(12;5;12.5) utreken."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7476
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMSQ(value;value;...)"
msgstr "SUMSQ(Weert;Weert;...)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7483
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMSQ(12;5;7) equals 218"
msgstr "SUMSQ(12;5;7) gifft \"218\" torüch"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7486
#, no-c-format
msgid "SUMSQ(12.5;2) equals 173"
msgstr "SUMSQ(12;5;2) gifft \"173\" torüch"

