#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TRUNC() function truncates a numeric value to a certain precision. If "
"the precision is omitted 0 is assumed."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon TRUNC() sniedt en numeersch Weert na en angeven Nauigkeit af. "
"Wenn keen Nauigkeit angeven is, warrt \"0\" vermoodt."

