#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The CHIDIST() function returns the probability value from the indicated Chi "
"square that a hypothesis is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon CHIDIST() gifft den Wohrschienlichkeitsweert vun dat angeven "
"Chi-Quadraat torüch, dat en Vermoden beglöövt warrt."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"CHIDIST compares the Chi square value to be given for a random sample that "
"is calculated from the sum of (observed value-expected value)^2/expected "
"value for all values with the theoretical Chi square distribution and "
"determines from this the probability of error for the hypothesis to be "
"tested."
msgstr ""
"CHIDIST vergliekt den Weert vun Chi-Quadraat för en tofällig Steekproov ut "
"de Summ vun \"(beluert Weert-verwacht Weert)^2/verwacht Weert\" för all "
"Weerten mit mööglich Chi-Quadraatverdelen un reekt dor de "
"Fehlerwohrschienlichkeit för de Vermoden mit ut, de pröövt warrn schall."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7705
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHIDIST(number;degrees_freedom)"
msgstr "CHIDIST(Tall;Freeheitgraad)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:7710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Degrees of freedom"
msgstr "Freeheitgraad"

