#, no-c-format
msgid "INVBINO"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:8184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The INVBINO() function returns the negative binomial distribution. The first "
"parameter is the number of trials, the second parameter is the number of "
"failures, and the third is the probability of failure. The number of trials "
"should be larger than the number of failures and the probability should be "
"smaller or equal to 1."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon INVBINO() gifft de negative binoomsch Verdelen torüch. De "
"eerste Parameter is de Tall vun Versöken, de twete de Tall vun Fehlslään, de "
"drüdde de Fehlslaagwohrschienlichkeit. De Tall vun Versöken schall grötter "
"wesen as de Tall vun Fehlslään un de Wohrschienlichkeit schall lütter oder "
"liek 1 wesen."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:8189
#, no-c-format
msgid "INVBINO(trials;failure;prob_of_failure)"
msgstr "INVBINO(Versöök;Fehlslään;Fehlslaagwohrschienlichkeit)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:8194 functions.docbook:8407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of failures"
msgstr "Fehlertall"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:8195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Probability of failure"
msgstr "Fehlslaagwohrschienlichkeit"

