#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:8533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PERCENTILE() function returns the x-th sample percentile of data values "
"in Data. A percentile returns the scale value for a data series which goes "
"from the smallest (alpha=0) to the largest value (alpha=1) of a data series. "
"For alpha = 25%, the percentile means the first quartile; alpha = 50% is the "
"MEDIAN. Blank cells will be considered as a zero, and cells with text will "
"be ignored."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon PERCENTILE() gifft dat x-te Musterperzentil vun Datenweerten "
"binnen \"Daten\" torüch. En Perzentil gifft en Skalenweert vun en Datenreeg "
"ehr lüttsten (alpha=0) bet na ehr gröttsten (alpha=1) Weert ut. Is alpha = "
"25%, denn bedüüdt \"Perzentil\" dat eerste Quantil; alpha = 50% is de "
"Dörsnitt. Leddig Zellen warrt as Null ankeken, un Textzellen warrt övergahn."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:8538
#, no-c-format
msgid "PERCENTILE(data;alpha)"
msgstr "PERCENTILE(Daten;alpha)"

