#, no-c-format
msgid "SEARCH"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:10101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The SEARCH() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text."
msgstr ""
"De Funkschoon SEARCH() söökt en Text \"Sööktext\" binnen de Tekenkeed "
"\"binnen_dissen_Text\" un gifft \"Sööktext\" sien Startpositschoon af dat "
"eerste linke Teken binnen \"binnen_dissen_Text\" ut."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:10102 functions.docbook:10135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use wildcard characters, question mark (?) and asterisk (*). A "
"question mark matches any single character, an asterisk matches any "
"sequences of characters."
msgstr ""
"Platzhollers sünd Fraagteken (?) un Steern (*). En Fraagteken steiht för "
"enkelte Tekens un en Steern för jichtenseen Tekenkeed."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:10103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter start_num specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 1. If start_num is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 1. SEARCH does not distinguish between uppercase and lowercase "
"letters."
msgstr ""
"De Parameter \"Startnummer\" gifft dat Teken an, af dat de Söök start. Dat "
"eerste Teken is Teken Nr. 1. Ahn \"Startnummer\" warrt \"1\" annahmen. "
"SEARCH ünnerscheedt nich twischen Groot- un Lüttschrieven."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:10108
#, no-c-format
msgid "SEARCH(find_text;within_text;start_num)"
msgstr "SEARCH(Sööktext;binnen_dissen_Text;Startnummer)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:10114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specified index to start the search"
msgstr "Angeven Index för den Söökanfang"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:10117
#, no-c-format
msgid "SEARCH(\"e\";\"Statements\";6) returns 7"
msgstr "SEARCH(\"e\";\"Kommentaren\";6) gifft \"10\" torüch"

